number of other possibilities in this position. We will take a look at these
in the theory section.} Be8 $1 {This is a good move. It has two main goals: 1)
Increasing the pressure against White's d-pawn. Black can now play ...Qd7 and ...Rd8. --- 2) Black was weak on the b1-h7 diagonal and had to think of a way
to meet Be4 and Qc2. Now Black can successfully meet this plan with ...Bg6.}
