Other options:} 10. e4 Nxe4 11. Nxe4 fxe4 12. Bxe4 e5 13. Bg2 {is equal.}) (10.
Qc2 Na6 11. a3 Ng4 $5 {. We have seen this idea before, and now} 12. e4 {may
