playing Nf4-Nd3 and with the other knight Nd2-Nf3. --- Black has not played ...d5 yet, so it should be in his favour to play ...d6 and ...e5, limiting the
activity of White's knight on h3 and taking control of the e5-square.} O-O 6.
O-O d6 $1 {. White now has three choices:} 7. -- ({a)} 7. Nf4) ({b)} 7. b3 $1)
({c)} 7. Nc3 $6) *

