very weak on the light squares. --- Of course, there are downsides to this
plan. For example, White neglects his development and as a consequence, his
kingside will eventually become weak due to its lack of defence. --- First of
all, let's see some examples of just how dangerous White's initiative can
become.} Nf6 {A natural move, but possibly a mistake.} (2... d5) ({and} 2... d6
