6. Bg5 g6 7. f3 Nf6 8. Nc3 c6 9. Qd2 Be6 {In exchange for a pawn, White enjoys
a space advantage, better development and attacking chances on the kingside.}
10. O-O-O Nbd7 11. Kb1 Bg7 12. Nh3 $1 {The knight heads for the f4-square
