, when the game could have continued} Qb6 5. Rb1 Nd7 $1 6. Bd3 g6 7. h4 Bg7 8.
h5 h6 9. Bf4 g5 10. Bh2 e5 $1 11. Bxf5 exd4 12. exd4 Ne7 {and Black has made
